sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant GA as GitHub Actions
    participant TF as Terraform
    participant Fabric as Microsoft Fabric
    participant State as Azure Blob (State)

    Note over Dev,State: Pull Request Flow (Plan)
    Dev->>GH: Push branch, open PR
    GH->>GA: Trigger plan workflow
    GA->>GA: az login (OIDC)
    GA->>TF: terraform init
    TF->>State: Download state
    GA->>TF: terraform plan
    TF->>Fabric: Read current config (API)
    TF-->>GA: Plan output (changes detected)
    GA->>GH: Post plan as PR comment

    Note over Dev,State: Review & Approval
    Dev->>GH: Request review
    GH-->>Dev: Reviewer approves PR

    Note over Dev,State: Merge Flow (Apply)
    Dev->>GH: Merge PR to main
    GH->>GA: Trigger apply workflow
    GA->>GA: az login (OIDC)
    GA->>TF: terraform init
    TF->>State: Download state
    GA->>TF: terraform apply -auto-approve
    TF->>Fabric: Create/update resources (API)
    TF->>State: Upload updated state
    TF-->>GA: Apply complete

    Note over Dev,State: Post-Apply Verification
    GA->>TF: terraform plan -detailed-exitcode
    TF-->>GA: Exit code 0 (no drift)
    GA->>GH: Status: success
